dc_title_s: Map of the world on Mercator's Projection: showing the direction of the ocean currents.
dc_description_s: Maps on verso: Map of the West Indies -- Jamaica -- Puerto Rico -- Map of Cuba -- Map of Havana Harbor. From "Indexed Atlas of the World". 1 map: col.; 87 x 65 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
